The largest Chinese companies merged against Alibaba
Chinese companies, among which is China's largest commercial real estate developer Dalian Wanda Group and Internet giants Tencent Holdings (social networks, messengers, etc.) and Baidu (the largest Chinese search engine) is creating a company that will compete in the online trading market with Alibaba.
