The ninth edition of "Mathematical Analysis" by Ron Larson, Bruce Edwards and Robert Hostetler costs about $290 in the price list, but the new copy can be purchased for $239.99 on the website Chegg.com, which specializes in selling textbooks.
Purchase of second-hand
